{"tid":1411387,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 人民幣離岸價首次跌穿7算　最低見7.1114","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T04:27:17.000Z","uid":297045,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"25a1a2c4cce688cf326f9fab83df3e4c1c5b8ea2","tid":1411387,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:35:22.000Z","msg":"2019-08-05 10:46<br />\n<br />\n人民幣今早繼續受壓，其中離岸價跌穿7，最低報7.1114，跌1,354點，最新報7.0786，跌1,026點子。今次是人民幣離岸首次跌穿7算。<br />\n<br />\n在岸價亦失守7算，最低見7.0345，最新報7.029，跌885點子。<br />\n<br />\n人民幣中間價今早低開229點，報6.9225。<br />\n<br />\n對於人民幣跌穿7算，《彭博》引述瑞穗亞洲外匯策略師張建泰指出，由於美國暫停貿易談判，所以人民銀行無需要再促使人民幣穩定。<br />\n<br />\n報道亦引述澳洲國民銀行亞洲市場策略主管Christy Tan指出，目前在岸及離岸價均跌穿7算，反映出是應對美國政府剛宣布的關稅，又認為只有出現失序情況下，如匯價大幅波動才會出手干預。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/360116/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E9%9B%A2%E5%B2%B8%E5%83%B9%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E8%B7%8C%E7%A9%BF7%E7%AE%97-%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E%E8%A6%8B7-1114-%E8%B7%8C1354%E9%BB%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F360116%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25B2%25B8%25E5%2583%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E8%25B7%258C%25E7%25A9%25BF7%25E7%25AE%2597-%25E6%259C%2580%25E4%25BD%258E%25E8%25A6%258B7-1114-%25E8%25B7%258C1354%25E9%25BB%259E&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEInGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=dbf72fa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/360116/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E9%9B%A2%E5%B2%B8%E5%83%B9%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E8%B7%8C%E7%A9%BF7%E7%AE%97-%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E%E8%A6%8B7-1114-%E8%B7%8C1354%E9%BB%9E</a>"},{"pid":"2785e92e6fb3baf93971c0857da40e943fbea079","tid":1411387,"uid":35430,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:41:04.000Z","msg":"人民弊跌到變印度盾班大陸豬都死唔去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ccae0823493eab8e1d2826fbe9